{"info":{"author":"Florian Schulze","author_email":"mail@florian-schulze.net","bugtrack_url":null,"classifiers":["Development Status :: 4 - Beta","Intended Audience :: Developers","License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License","Programming Language :: Python :: 3","Programming Language :: Python :: 3 :: Only","Programming Language :: Python :: 3.6","Programming Language :: Python :: 3.7","Programming Language :: Python :: 3.8","Programming Language :: Python :: 3.9","Topic :: System :: Software Distribution","Topic :: Utilities"],"description":"setuptools-changelog-shortener\n==============================\n\nThis setuptools plugin allows shortening the number of changelog entries to use for the ``long_description`` metadata in Python packages.\n\n\nUsage\n-----\n\nFirst, ensure that ``setuptools_changelog_shortener`` is present in your build requirements.\n\n.. code:: toml\n\n    # pyproject.toml\n    [build-system]\n    requires = [\"setuptools>=45\", \"wheel\", \"setuptools_changelog_shortener\"]\n\nTo enable changelog shortening, add the following section to your ``pyproject.toml``:\n\n.. code:: toml\n\n    # pyproject.toml\n    [tool.setuptools_changelog_shortener]\n    read_from = \"CHANGELOG.rst\"\n    write_to = \"CHANGELOG.short.rst\"\n\nThen you use the ``CHANGELOG.short.rst`` file for your ``long_description`` metadata field.\n\nAdditional options are:\n\n``count``\n    The number of changelog entries to include.\n    Defaults to ``5``.\n\n``delimiter``\n    The delimiter to look for in each entry.\n    Defaults to the ``^--+`` regular expression to find docutils titles using ``-`` characters.\n\n``title``\n    The title to add to the top of the shortened CHANGELOG file.\n    Defaults to ``Changelog\\n=========``.\n\n\nChangelog\n=========\n\n0.2.0 (unreleased)\n------------------\n\n- Fix error when ``count`` is bigger or equal the number of changelog entries.\n\n- Add ``tomli`` to build requirements.\n\n\n0.1.0 (2022-02-07)\n------------------\n\n- Initial release.\n\n\n","description_content_type":"text/x-rst","docs_url":null,"download_url":"","downloads":{"last_day":-1,"last_month":-1,"last_week":-1},"dynamic":null,"home_page":"https://github.com/fschulze/setuptools-changelog-shortener","keywords":"","license":"MIT","maintainer":"","maintainer_email":"","name":"setuptools-changelog-shortener","package_url":"https://pypi.org/project/setuptools-changelog-shortener/","platform":"","project_url":"https://pypi.org/project/setuptools-changelog-shortener/","project_urls":{"Bug Tracker":"https://github.com/fschulze/setuptools-changelog-shortener/issues","Homepage":"https://github.com/fschulze/setuptools-changelog-shortener","Source Code":"https://github.com/fschulze/setuptools-changelog-shortener"},"provides_extra":null,"release_url":"https://pypi.org/project/setuptools-changelog-shortener/0.2.0/","requires_dist":["setuptools (>=45)","tomli (>=1.0)"],"requires_python":">=3.6","summary":"\"setuptools-changelog-shortener: add only newest changelog entries to long_description\"","version":"0.2.0","yanked":false,"yanked_reason":null},"last_serial":12811831,"releases":{"0.1.0":[{"comment_text":"","digests":{"blake2b_256":"be39870efa8523b0e815c7e155eceefbe6d8a5d2fa16dfd8db6ed05d532209e2","md5":"ca3e1d67299ae609bacda3630853915c","sha256":"4997ff35c8c6235343385e7a2877e31542b1fca0c725ffea544092e40c0696aa"},"downloads":-1,"filename":"setuptools_changelog_shortener-0.1.0-py3-none-any.whl","has_sig":false,"md5_digest":"ca3e1d67299ae609bacda3630853915c","packagetype":"bdist_wheel","python_version":"3","requires_python":">=3.6","size":4163,"upload_time":"2022-02-07T11:49:53","upload_time_iso_8601":"2022-02-07T11:49:53.548166Z","url":"https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/be/39/870efa8523b0e815c7e155eceefbe6d8a5d2fa16dfd8db6ed05d532209e2/setuptools_changelog_shortener-0.1.0-py3-none-any.whl","yanked":false,"yanked_reason":null},{"comment_text":"","digests":{"blake2b_256":"82e2122f71aeeeaedeb58645c68ade250a9fb17bf298ab0377abe4936d0fc1a1","